KNOW WHAT THE UPCOMING GLOBAL GIFT EVENTS ARE

   Global Gift Home, Casa Global Gift, is now a reality. The Townhall of
   Marbella has successfully ordered the concession of La Panocha house to
   the Global Gift Foundation for a term of 30 years. Global Gift
   Foundation will remodel this home into a state of the art treatment
   centre for children with rare and chronic diseases which will be the
   home to, but limited to, the following associations: Adisol (Asociación
   de Diabéticos de la Costa del Sol), ADAHIMAR (Asociación Social de
   Trastornos para Déficit de Atención e Hiperactividad), CADI (Centro de
   Atención a la Diversidad Infantil), Association Against Cystic Fibrosis
   and Bubble and Dreams (rare and undiagnosed diseases).

   IFRAME:
   https://www.youtube.com/embed/OH5Kl8ohbDI?start=3&feature=oembed

