Eva Longoria. Philanthropist

   The Eva Longoria Foundation reflects an active social conscience and
   complete dedication to Latina Women and their families. Global Gift
   Foundation believes in this cause and admires the work of its founder,
   her time dedication and a tireless fight to succeed.
   Eva Longoria Foundation
   Ricky Martin Foundation

Ricky Martin. Honorary Ambassador

   The Ricky Martin Foundation carries out much needed difficult but
   necessary work, worthy of the highest praise. For this reason, Global
   Gift Foundation provides help whenever the opportunity arises.

   Ricky Martin is an extraordinary human being that leaves large
   footprints on his trails filled with well-defined values; his social
   commitment and dedication to the youngest of our communities form part
   of his qualities, something which Global Gift recognizes and values.

Subscribe to our mailing list

   The Global Gift Foundation is a philanthropic non-profit organization
   that aims to create a positive impact on the lives of children, women
   and families who are in need. We help meet basic needs in the lives of
   vulnerable groups by creating campaigns, partnerships with major brands
   and ambassadors and beneficiary institutions and institutions that
   allow an impact of social transformation. Subscribe now and keep
   updated on what we do. Thank you!
